data.text:
Learn about the county of Tyne & Wear in the North East of England, including the main locations, things to do and places to see. It is home to the cities of Newcastle upon Tyne and Sunderland, as well as the large town Gateshead.

Across our website, we’ll include pages of businesses, education and local information for Tyne and Wear.
